    "persona_panel": "AI Persona chat panel - engage ah authentic conversations he historical figures, scientists, literary characters, asilole custom personas. Uses advanced AI ah simulate period-accurate speech a kah, knowledge, le perspectives. Perfect caah primary source analysis, perspective-taking, le empathy-building exercises. Supports multiple response modes: Ah-Character (fully immersive), Educational (he learning scaffolds), asilole Mixed (balanced approach).",
    "persona_card": "AI persona ready caah conversation. pakhat fate card langhter character's name, caan period, le expertise area. Hnen ah thawk interview - AI will respond authentically based cung their historical context, beliefs, le knowledge. Hman personas caah primary source analysis, perspective-taking exercises, asilole creative tialnak inspiration.",
    "persona_generate_button": "Generate AI personas automatically from nangmah source content. system analyzes nangmah text ah theih khawh key figures, historical periods, asilole character archetypes le creates authentic conversational partners. Tuah personas include accurate biographical details, period-appropriate vocabulary, le contextual knowledge limitations (they won't know kong events after their caan).",
    "persona_select_button": "Thim hi persona ah begin nangmah interview asilole conversation. Once selected, nang'll lut immersive chat interface khoika nang can ask biahalnak, explore their perspective, le earn XP caah meaningful exchanges. AI responds based cung character's historical knowledge, personality, le cultural context.",
    "persona_back_btn": "Return ah persona selection screen ah thim different character. nangmah current conversation progress si automatically khoh cang, le nang can return ah zulh it later. hi allows exploring multiple perspectives cung a kanglawng historical kong.",
    "persona_custom_instructions": "Tel lakhmi requirements caah how persona should behave during conversations. Examples: focus cung lakhmi caan period, emphasize certain beliefs asilole values, maintain particular speech a kah, asilole limit responses ah historically accurate knowledge. sayama can hman hi ah align personas he lakhmi learning objectives.",
    "persona_response_mode": "Thim how persona responds ah create different learning experiences. IN CHARACTER: Fully immersive historical voice he no modern explanations. EDUCATIONAL: Character speaks sihmanhsehlaw includes learning scaffolds, vocabulary support, le context. MIXED: Balanced approach he authentic voice plus occasional clarifications. Thim based cung sianginn caa readiness le learning goals.",
    "persona_free_response": "Type nangmah own ka-ended response instead i selecting from pre-written options. Free response mode promotes creative expression, critical thinking, le authentic dialogue skills. Responses si analyzed caah historical a hman, empathy, le depth i inquiry. Higher-quality biahalnak earn tampin XP.",
    "persona_hints_toggle": "Langhter asilole thup response suggestions le conversation hints. When enabled, system provides scaffolded biahalnak starters, historical context biapenh, le engagement suggestions. Helpful caah sianginn caa thar ah historical inquiry asilole those needing support he ka-ended questioning. sayama can disable hints caah tampin advanced assessment scenarios.",
    "persona_show_hints": "Langhter helpful hints caah engaging he persona. Hints include historically relevant biahalnak ah ask, topics character would find interesting, le biapenh mah lead ah deeper understanding. A ngan caah sianginn caa who need scaffolding asilole aren't sure how ah begin historical interview.",
    "persona_submit_btn": "Thlah nangmah message ah persona character. nangmah biahalnak asilole response si analyzed caah relevance le depth. AI persona will respond authentically based cung their historical context, knowledge, le personality. Well-crafted biahalnak mah langhter historical understanding earn bonus XP.",
    "persona_close": "Khar persona conversation panel. nangmah chat history le earned XP si automatically khoh cang. nang can resume hi conversation later from History tab.",
    "persona_close_title": "Khar Persona Chat",
    "persona_reflection_input": "Tial nangmah reflection cung conversation caah assessment. Reflect cung what nang learned kong historical figure, how their perspective differs from modern viewpoints, le how hi conversation changed nangmah understanding. Reflections si evaluated using rubric aligned ah historical thinking skills le can earn significant XP.",
    "persona_conclude": "End conversation le generate comprehensive tampin tang i nangmah discussion. tampin tang includes: key topics covered, historical insights gained, quality i nangmah biahalnak, empathy demonstrated, le XP earned. hi tampin tang can be exported caah assessment, added ah sianginn caa portfolios, asilole used as tialnak prompt caah reflection activities.",
    "persona_save_chat": "Khoh hi conversation ah review asilole share later. Saved chats preserve tlangpi dialogue, XP earned, timestamps, le any reflections. Hman khoh cang chats caah sianginn caa portfolios, assessment tehna, sianginn discussions, asilole exemplar models. Saved conversations can be exported as PDF asilole shared he a dang sianginn caa.",
    "persona_topic_spark": "Get conversation starter asilole kong suggestion when nang're si lo sure what ah ask. system generates historically relevant biahalnak based cung persona's background, expertise, le caan period. A ngan caah overcoming writer's block asilole discovering thar angles ah explore ah nangmah historical inquiry.",
    "persona_auto_send": "Automatically thlah nangmah message when nang dinh typing caah few tikcu. Creates tampin natural conversational flow, especially when using voice dictation. Disable hi if nang prefer ah review le thlen messages before sending, asilole if nang need tampin caan ah compose thoughtful responses.",
    "analysis_generate_button": "Analyze nangmah source text caah reading level, complexity, le features.",
    "analysis_check_accuracy": "Fact-check source content against reliable references.",
    "outline_generate_button": "Generate visual organizer from nangmah source content.",
    "timeline_generate_button": "Generate timeline i events from nangmah source content.",
    "timeline_topic": "main kong asilole theme i timeline being tuah. AI creates historically accurate events based cung hi kong le nangmah source content. Example topics: American Revolution, Life Cycle i Stars, Shakespeare's Career. Events si automatically ordered chronologically caah sequencing practice.",
    "timeline_count": "Number i events ah include ah timeline. tampin events create longer, tampin detailed timelines sihmanhsehlaw increase difficulty. Recommended: 4-6 events caah beginners, 8-10 caah intermediate, 12+ caah advanced sianginn ca. Events si draggable caah sequencing practice after chan.",
