      "no_matches": "Aa tlakmi a um lo.",
      "iep_goal_bank_fraction_specific": "🎯 IEP Goal Bank — ṭhen kong lawng",
      "pre_formatted_smart_goals_for_iep_team": "IEP team caah a timhmi SMART goal. Goal pakhat cio nih CCSS standard ah aa pehtlaih, AlloFlow chungah hmasawnnak-zohkhenhnak data hmun a langhter, cun accommodation a fcommi a langhter. Na siangngakchia caah copy law remh.",
      "show_accommodations_and_progress_monit": "Accommodation le hmasawnnak zohkhenhnak langhter",
