      "a_snail_moves_at_about_1_40_of_a_mile_": "Chiimel cu suimilam khat ah mile 1/40 hrawng a kal. Mile 1 kal awkah suimilam 40 a hlawh lai.",
      "a_kangaroo_can_leap_a_distance_about_3": "Kangaroo cu peihnak khat ah a pum saunak 3/2 hrawng a peih khawh.",
