      "a_giant_tortoise_can_live_to_150_years": "Tuahpi nganpi cu kum 150+ a nun khawh. Kum 100 a rammi tuahpi cu a nun khawhmi 2/3 a nung cang.",
      "animal_fractions": "🐾 Sarang ṭhen",
