      "frequency_modulation_fm_synthesis_uses": "Frequency Modulation (FM) synthesis nih oscillator pakhat (modulator) hman in a dang (carrier) frequency kha a rangmi in a thlen. Modulator:carrier ratio nih harmonic content a khiah. Ratio a fawimi (1:1, 2:1, 3:1) nih harmonic tones a chuahter. Ratio a harsami nih metallic, bell-like asiloah inharmonic sounds a chuahter. Yamaha DX7 nih 1983 ah FM a hlawhtling ter.",
