      "an_arpeggiator_plays_the_notes_of_a_ch": "🔬 Arpeggiator nih chord note pawl kha pakhat cio in remh in a tuk. \"A cung\" cu a niang in a sang, thazang a sang a ser. \"A niang\" cu a nuam, tiva bantuk ruahnak a pek. A rannak nih rannak a uk (a tlawm = a rang). Gate nih note pakhat cio zeitluk a ram a uk (100% = legato, 10% = staccato). Classic trance arp awkah rannak=100ms + octaves 4 + up pattern zuam!",
