      "build_1_2_1_3_with_rods_using_a_6_rod_": "Build 1/2 + 1/3 with rods, using a 6-rod (dark green) as the whole. Half of 6 is 3 (light green). A third is 2 (red). Combined: 5. Read as 5/6.",
      "subtracting_negatives": "Subtracting negatives",
