      "space_exploration_is_in_a_renaissance_": "Van hawlrelnak cu a thar tthan lio a si. Ram thar (India, Japan, UAE), bu thar (SpaceX, Blue Origin), rian thar (Europa Clipper, Artemis, JWST). Cunglei zoh — i lungthin chiah.",
