      "astronomers_report_events_in_utc_so_ob": "Van science mi nih vawlei pumpi zohnak innṭha nih an i tahchunh khawh nakah UTC in an chim. SpaceX cu UTC in a chuah. NASA rian cu UTC in a si.",
      "maine_utc_5_est_or_utc_4_edt_london_ut": "Maine: UTC-5 (EST) asiloah UTC-4 (EDT). London: UTC+0 (GMT) asiloah UTC+1 (BST). Japan: UTC+9.",
      "tip_when_you_read_an_astronomy_event_t": "Ralrin: van science caanzin na rel tikah, UTC a si maw asiloah na hmun caan a si maw ti zoh peng.",
      "utc_replaced_gmt_in_1972_based_on_atom": "UTC nih 1972 ah GMT a thlak. Vawlei pumpi ram lab i atom suimilam cungah a hmang, an i pumh. A herh tikah second an telh.",
