      "harmony_desc": "Aw aa remmi le aa rem lomi kha tahchunh, frequency ratio kha milem he pehtlaih, hla pehtlaihnak kha hmuhnak aa remnak ah thlen",
      "contrast": "Aa Dannak",
      "wcag_contrast_checker_for_accessibilit": "Mi vialte nih an hmuh khawh nakhnga WCAG rong aa dannak checker",
      "educational_concepts": "💡 Cawnnak Ruahnak",
      "color_theory_additive_vs_subtractive_m": "Rong ruahnak (a i telhmi le a i lakmi chawhnak, rong aa remmi, HSL/RGB), nambat in a kawimi milem (hypotrochoids, Lissajous), fractals le amah he aa lohmi, tessellation geometry, op art ah mit nih zeitindah a hmuh, WCAG hmuh khawhnak phunglam, le computer milem. Tool pakhat cio nih a dawtnak chungah a ummi nambat kha an in cawnpiak.",
