      "canvas_summary_stock_market_empty": "Ṭhenmi dawr milem hmun cu dawr thar caah a i timh cang. Man tuanbia le na ngeihmi ṭhenmi hmuh awkah dawr entelnak thawk.",
      "canvas_summary_business": "Sumdawr zohkhenhnak nih tangka, minthannak, pum khat man le hlawknak, man aa tlaknak hmun, le nifate hlawknak tuanbia kha a langhter.",
      "day": "ni",
      "canvas_summary_business_empty": "Sumdawr zohkhenhnak hmun a hoi rih. Tangka, minthannak, le nifate hlawknak hikah hmuh awkah a tang ah sumdawr thawk.",
      "canvas_summary_macro": "Ram sum le pai zohkhenhnak nih GDP ṭhannak, man sannak, puh man, rian ngeih lonak, sumdawr aa remnak, le phunglam tuanbia kha a langhter.",
      "canvas_summary_inquiry": "Phunglam holhchiannak nih makro chuahmi entelnak sernak caah phunglam hnenhnak pali a hmang. GDP, man sannak, le rian ngeih lonak lengmangnak tahchunh awkah a tang i phunglam bar kha hmang.",
